data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Immaculate 2021 single level home located in a serene neighborhood on a superbly positioned corner lot - without HOA! The interior boasts sleek white shaker cabinetry, lustrous granite countertops, stainless steel appliances. Additional features include vaulted ceilings, large rooms with lots of closet space, and AC. Enjoy easy upkeep with a low-maintenance yard and sprinkler system. Located near Willamette Towncenter, Starbucks, parks, schools and I-5 for ultimate convenience.
